  <para style="mt1">MARŨA MA KEERĨ MA JOHANA</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Marũa maya ma Keerĩ ma Johana maandĩkĩirwo mũtumia mũthuure hamwe na ciana ciake. Arutani a maheeni nĩmahũthagĩra ciĩko cia ũtugi iria cionanagio nĩ Akristiano, na makahũthĩra mweke ũcio kũrutana ũrutani wao mũhĩtanu. Johana nĩakaanirie Akristiano matikanyiitage andũ ta acio ũgeni kwao mĩciĩ tondũ maarĩ athũkia a wĩtĩkio (7-11).</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Mũtũmwo Johana.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Kwĩmenyithania <char style="ior"><ref loc="2JN 1:1-3">1-3</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mũtũũrĩre wa wendani <char style="ior"><ref loc="2JN 1:4-6">4-6</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kũregana na Mũmena-Kristũ na mũheenania <char style="ior"><ref loc="2JN 1:7-13">7-13</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 8:32">Joh 8:32</ref>; <ref loc="3JN 1:1">3Joh 1</ref></char>
    </note>Kuuma kũrĩ niĩ Mũthuuri wa Kanitha,</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Ndaandĩka marũa maya kũrĩ mũtumia ũrĩa mũthuure, o hamwe na ciana ciake, arĩa nyendete kũna kũna, na to niĩ nyiki, no nĩ hamwe na arĩa othe mamenyete ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma: <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:12">2Pet 1:12</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 1:8">1Joh 1:8</ref></char></note>makamwenda tondũ wa ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma, ũrĩa ũtũũraga thĩinĩ witũ, o na ũgũtũũra na ithuĩ nginya tene:</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:7">Arom 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wega, na tha, na thayũ kuuma kũrĩ Ngai Ithe, na kuuma kũrĩ Jesũ Kristũ, o we Mũriũ wa Ithe witũ, irĩikaraga na ithuĩ thĩinĩ wa ũhoro wa ma, na wa wendo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="3JN 1:3">3Joh 3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩngenete mũno nĩkuona ciana imwe ciaku igĩthiĩ na njĩra ya ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma, o ta ũrĩa Ithe witũ aatwathire. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:7">1Joh 2:7</ref></char></note>Na rĩu, mũtumia ũyũ mwende, ti rĩathani rĩerũ ndĩrakwandĩkĩra, no nĩ rĩrĩa tũtũire narĩo kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria. Ngũũria atĩ twendanage mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:5">1Joh 2:5</ref></char></note>Naguo wendani nĩ atĩrĩ: Atĩ tũthiiage na njĩra ya gwathĩkĩra maathani make. O ta ũrĩa mũiguĩte kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria, rĩathani rĩake nĩ atĩ mũthiiage mũrĩ o na wendani ũcio.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1JN 2:8">1Joh 2:8</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:1">1Joh 4:1</ref></char>
    </note>Aheenania, aingĩ arĩa matetĩkĩtie atĩ Jesũ Kristũ ookire arĩ na mwĩrĩ, nĩmarorũũra gũkũ thĩ. Mũndũ ta ũcio nĩ mũheenania na nĩ mũmena-Kristũ. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:42">Math 10:42</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 10:29">Mar 10:29</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:8">1Akor 3:8</ref></char></note>Mwĩhũgagei nĩguo mũtigate kĩrĩa mũrutĩire wĩra, no mũtuĩke a gũkaaheo mũcaara wanyu ũrĩ wothe. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:23">1Joh 2:23</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:23">1Joh 2:23</ref></char></note>Mũndũ o wothe ũkĩraga njano akarega kũrũmĩrĩra ũrutani wa Kristũ, ũcio ndakoragwo na Ngai; no ũrĩa ũikaraga ũrutani-inĩ ũcio, we arĩ na Ithe witũ o na Mũriũ. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:17">Arom 16:17</ref></char></note>Mũndũ o wothe angĩũka kũrĩ inyuĩ arĩ na ũrutani ũngĩ tiga ũcio-rĩ, mũtikanamũnyiite ũgeni o na kana mũmwamũkĩre kwanyu mũciĩ. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 5:22">1Tim 5:22</ref></char></note>Mũndũ wothe ũngĩmwamũkĩra, nĩkũgwatanĩra magwatanĩire nake ciĩko ciake cia waganu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:29">Joh 3:29</ref>; <ref loc="3JN 1:13">3Joh 13</ref>, <ref loc="3JN 1:14">14</ref></char>
    </note>Ndĩ na maũndũ maingĩ ma kũmwandĩkĩra, no ndikwenda kũhũthĩra karatathi na rangi. Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, ndĩrehoka kũmũceerera njaranĩrie na inyuĩ tũkĩonanaga, nĩgeetha gĩkeno giitũ kĩiganĩre.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2JN 1:1">2Joh 1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩmwageithio nĩ ciana cia mwarĩ wa maitũguo ũrĩa mũthuure.</para>
